## Introduction

This article was written in markdown!

### How?

To use markdown instead of the standard fileformat you have to use the tag 'Filetype'
and set its value to 'Markdown' (not case sensitive).

### Limitations?

You will not have a table of contents with markdown (<em>yet</em>).